Package dataStructure.graph.hashMapGraph

Class HashMapGraph<K extends Comparable<K>>

java.lang.Object
dataStructure.graph.hashMapGraph.HashMapGraph<K>
Type Parameters:
K - the type of vertex keys in the graph, must implement Comparable interface
All Implemented Interfaces:
Graph<K>
public class HashMapGraph<K extends Comparable<K>> extends Object implements Graph<K>
A graph implementation using HashMap to store the adjacency map.
